mp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b.jpeg?fit=300%2C193&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b.jpeg?fit=750%2C482&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"750\" height=\"482\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b.jpeg?resize=750%2C482&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6859\" data-full-url=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b.jpeg?resize=750%2C482&#038;ssl=1\" data-link=\"/6-idees-pour-un-amenagement-sous-escalier/8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b/\" class=\"wp-image-6859\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b.jpeg?w=883&amp;ssl=1 883w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b.jpeg?resize=300%2C193&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/8111670293aa357db99177eedde00c4b.jpeg?resize=768%2C494&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></figure></li></ul></figure>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/6-idees-pour-un-amenagement-sous-escalier\\/\"}' style=\"height:61px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h3>Un coin détente sous son escalier, pour lire ou buller</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Quoi de mieux que s’étaler dans de gros coussins avec un bon bouquin et ne pas voir le temps passer ?<br>Pour une pause apaisante, aménagez un&nbsp;<strong>coin lecture</strong>&nbsp;ou une alcôve, et faites en un espace tranquille et douillet. Vous pouvez l’aménager avec une petite&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://hopfab.com/realisations?type=R%C3%A9sidentiel\">banquette sur-mesure</a></strong>, agrémentée d’un plaid, de gros coussins, et vous y emmitoufler pour dévorer votre livre favori. Cet espace sera aussi parfait pour une sieste express.<br>Faites en sorte que cet endroit soit chaleureux, inspirant, et profitez de réels moments de détente.</p>\n\n\n\n<div data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/6-idees-pour-un-amenagement-sous-escalier\\/\"}' style=\"height:11px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":1,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/next.wp.hopfab.com\\/6-idees-pour-un-amenagement-sous-escalier\\/\"}' class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img data-attachment-id=\"6861\" data-permalink=\"/6-idees-pour-un-amenagement-sous-escalier/58ec80936c18b9775308002d52806b39/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/58ec80936c18b9775308002d52806b39.jpeg?fit=1561%2C1708&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1561,1708\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"58ec80936c18b9775308002d52806b39\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/next.wp.hopfab.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/58